com.crawljax.core.state

Class StateVertex

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.crawljax.core.state.StateVertex
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class StateVertex
extends Object
implements Serializable
    The state vertex class which represents a state in the browser. This class implements the Iterable interface because on a StateVertex it is possible to iterate over the possible CandidateElements found in this state. When iterating over the possible candidate elements every time a candidate is returned its removed from the list so it is a one time only access to the candidates.
